com.basho.riak.client.core.query

Class BucketProperties

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.basho.riak.client.core.query.BucketProperties

  • public class BucketProperties
extends Object
    Bucket properties used for buckets and bucket types. Note that when instantiating a new instance there are no default values. Calling a getter for a specific property will return null if it has not been explicitly set. Unset properties are ignored when writing to a bucket or bucket type in Riak.
    Since:
    2.0
    Author:
    Brian Roach
